83
00:06:28,510 --> 00:06:29,790
Is it because of Qu Kai?

84
00:06:31,390 --> 00:06:33,200
Why is it because of him?

85
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:35,070
I have been single for a while.

86
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,880
