129
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:16,150
If you want food, go out the door
and turn right.

130
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,230
Sa,

131
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:20,000
it's me.

132
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:25,230
